{
  "stem": "2581.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my grandmother would get very upset, very upset, and she would let them know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I know she didn't, you know-- but [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she was a strong-minded person.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember we used to come to visit her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She would give us fruits, cut up pieces of apple, but it was with love.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I only later realized when I began to understand under what circumstances she lived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My father would always try to help her, and he did help, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He did help.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He helped the entire family, because he came from surroundings that were worse off than he was when he-- we had this tailor shop and we lived comfortably.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So he helped his family, and he wouldn't do a thing with that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Talking to his mother, she was a wise woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I'm sorry to say that one of the advices wasn't so good, because her mother's-- I mean, my mother's-- from my mother's family that lived in Argentina, they were very well off, had sent what was called a [NON-ENGLISH], you know, papers to go to Argentina for my father when I was one year old-- one years old.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my mother said, you go ahead, and I'll come later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But my father went for advice to his mother, and she said, you're going to go to a far country.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You'll become a goy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You'll have to work for someone else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Here, you have your own factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You're going away from the family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So my father listened to his mother, not to his wife, to the regret of the entire family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after the war, I was in contact with this-- with the family in Argentina, and they all reminded me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Says-- they said that everyone could have been saved.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
